    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lardons are cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely (no need to peel!)</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
