    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lardons are golden, add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pan with the <strong>sliced onion</strong>,<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>diced carrot </strong>and<strong> dried thyme</strong></p><p>Season with a crack of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until the onion has softened</p>",
