    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix</strong>,<strong> tomato paste </strong>and <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>in 250ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>stock</strong></p>",
