    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained cannellini beans </strong>to the pan with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then reduce to medium-high and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>bacon & hearty bean filling</strong></p>",
